name: Zebra Tee
description:
Oh, I’m exhausted. I’ve been on this street a thousand times. It’s never looked so strange. The faces…so cold. In the distance a child is crying…fatherless…a bastard child, perhaps.
It’s a hot night. The mind races.
You think about your knife, the only friend who hasn’t betrayed you, the only friend who won’t be dead by sunup. Comfort. Style. Wear-ability. Sleep tight in your quilted chambray Zebra Tee.
